[color=#ffff00][size=4]Description:[/size][/color]
Akaviri Dungeon Tileset - Modder's Resource v0.1 ENG
This tileset allows you to create an Akaviri dungeons. Also it adds new test location that demonstrates variants of tileset blocks combining.
You can reach it in Editor Smoke Test Cell location (coc qasmoke).
More detailed info on this tileset is in ingame book that you can obtain in the new Akaviri test dungeon.
